This is a library for generating PDF documents with Lua 5.2. It is based on
the PDFlib Lite library is available at
	http://www.pdflib.com/download/free-software/pdflib-lite-7/

To try the library, edit Makefile to reflect your installation of Lua and
PDFlib Lite. Then run make. This will build the library and run a simple test.
For detailed installation instructions, see
        http://www.tecgraf.puc-rio.br/~lhf/ftp/lua/install.html

There is no manual but the binding follows the PDFlib Lite interface closely;
read the PDFlib manual. The examples in test.lua show the library in action.

This code is hereby placed in the public domain.
PDFlib Lite has its own license.
Please send comments, suggestions, and bug reports to lhf@tecgraf.puc-rio.br .

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

